Class MessageChannelPoolMap<M extends AbstractMessage,K>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibasco.agql.core.transport.pool.MessageChannelPoolMap<M,K>
  • Type Parameters:
    M - An AbstractMessage that will be used as a reference for our key lookup
    K - The actual key that will be used for the underlying ChannelPoolMap implementation. The type of this key should be the same type returned by our key resolver.
